---
---

<section class="hero" aria-label="Campaign hero">
  <div class="hero-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="container hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-tagline-pill">8th Bristol District · Massachusetts</div>
      <h1 class="hero-headline">Believe in Steve.</h1>
      <p class="hero-subheadline">
        Serving the 8th Bristol District through practical leadership,
        community engagement, and responsive constituent service.
      </p>
      <p class="hero-body">
        A lifelong South Coast resident, Steve Ouellette has spent decades
        serving local communities through municipal leadership, regional
        planning, infrastructure initiatives, and public service. Before
        joining the Massachusetts House of Representatives, Steve served
        multiple terms on the Westport Select Board, held leadership roles
        in economic development and infrastructure oversight, and worked in
        public facilities management and the skilled trades. Today, he
        remains focused on supporting local communities, strengthening
        public infrastructure, and ensuring residents have access to
        responsive constituent services throughout the 8th Bristol District.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#signup" class="btn btn-hero-primary">Sign up for updates</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary--light">Contact Steve</a>
      </div>

      <p class="hero-location">
        <span aria-hidden="true">📍</span>
        Proudly serving Acushnet, parts of Fall River and New Bedford, Freetown, and Westport.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-tertiary">
        <a href="/constituent-services">Constituent Services →</a>
        <span class="hero-tertiary-sep" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
        <a href="/constituent-services#citation">Request a citation or resolution →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-wave-wrap" aria-hidden="true">
    <img src="/images/hero-wave.svg" alt="" class="hero-wave-img" />
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    background-image: url('/images/campaign-supporters.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center top;
    color: var(--color-white);
    padding-top: 5rem;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Single gradient layer: opaque dark panel left → completely clear right */
  .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to right,
      rgba(8, 20, 42, 0.93) 0%,
      rgba(8, 20, 42, 0.93) 40%,
      rgba(8, 20, 42, 0.50) 58%,
      rgba(8, 20, 42, 0.0) 74%,
      rgba(8, 20, 42, 0.0) 100%
    );
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding-bottom: 4.5rem;
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .hero-tagline-pill {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.9rem;
    background-color: var(--color-red);
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em;
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .hero-headline {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .hero-subheadline {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: rgba(242, 243, 244, 0.9);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .hero-body {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: rgba(242, 243, 244, 0.78);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: none;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .btn-hero-primary {
    background-color: var(--color-navy);
    color: var(--color-white);
    border-color: var(--color-navy);
  }

  .btn-hero-primary:hover {
    background-color: #0a2e4a;
    border-color: #0a2e4a;
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .hero-location {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(242, 243, 244, 0.75);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .hero-tertiary {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .hero-tertiary a {
    color: rgba(242, 243, 244, 0.75);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .hero-tertiary a:hover {
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .hero-tertiary-sep {
    color: rgba(242, 243, 244, 0.4);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .hero-wave-wrap {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    line-height: 0;
    margin-top: -2px;
  }

  .hero-wave-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 60px;
    display: block;
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .hero {
      padding-top: 3rem;
    }

    .hero-inner {
      padding-bottom: 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
